data.description: Feast your eyes on this gem! Introducing a spacious 2,200 sq ft sanctuary nestled on a prime corner lot in Temple! Dive into summer with your very own in-ground pool and when the temperatures drop, cozy up next to the built-in fireplace. Enjoy the shade from the magnificent oak tree adorning the front yard and cherish moments on the lovely covered back porch. Boasting 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a dedicated office space, this house is not just a home: it's a lifestyle. Location? PERFECT! Just minutes from Baylor Scott & White Hospital and I-35. Enjoy convenience with multiple parks, delicious restaurants, and shopping experiences right at your fingertips. Schedule a private showing today!
